# Demo: ConfigService integration
#
# Copy to `.env.local` and uncomment the URL to switch from Dexie-only
# mode to REST mode. With this set, the demo's ConfigManager mirrors
# every write to the REST backend at apps/config-service-server.
#
# Reads always come from Dexie for speed. Failed REST writes queue in
# the PENDING_SYNC table and retry every 10 seconds.
#
# Start the server first:
#   cd apps/config-service-server && npm run dev   # listens on :3001
#
# Then uncomment:
# VITE_CONFIG_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:3001/api/v1
